``` Compact SPL fixture: café, λ, 東京, 🚀, and astral 𝌆.
Every block and quoted state closes before the pipeline ends. ```
search index=web sourcetype=access_combined earliest=-24h
| rex field=_raw "status=(?<status>\\d+) duration=(?<duration>\\d+)"
| eval city=coalesce(city, "東京"), owner=lower(user)
| eval label=if(status>=500, "café failure 🚀", 'normal λ 𝌆')
| where status>=400 AND duration>100
| lookup service_catalog service OUTPUTNEW team tier
| stats count AS requests avg(duration) AS latency
        values(city) AS cities dc(owner) AS owners BY service, status
| eventstats sum(requests) AS all_requests BY team
| eval share=round(100*requests/all_requests, 2)
| sort 0 -requests, service
| table service status team tier requests latency share cities owners
| head 20
| `comment(the macro comment is also fully closed)`
